{
  "texts": [
    "To enhance the feature embedding ability of nodes, the upstream node features are con-catenated as the input of the fully connected layer.",
    "Graphs G can be represented by the triplets G,,,, =",
    ", where V are set of unordered nodes, ε 1 and ε 2 represent the edge sets of semantic networks and structural networks, φ ε",
    "is a mapping function based on the node position relationships, ϕ ε: 2 2 → R is a mapping function based on the text content between nodes, R 1 and R 2 are a collection of node relationship types.",
    "A and D are adjacency matrix and degree matrix, respectively."
  ]
}